---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Gaia Impact Fund | Capital Regenerativo"
  description="Capital al servicio de la vida. El fondo estratégico que moviliza y despliega recursos hacia la regeneración ecológica a gran escala."
  keywords={["Gaia Impact Fund", "capital regenerativo", "inversión de impacto", "fondos bioregionales", "regeneración ecológica", "finanzas regenerativas"]}
  schemaType={["WebPage", "Organization"]}
>
  
  <!-- Top Navigation Shell -->
  <nav class="fixed top-0 w-full z-50 bg-[#fefee5]/80 backdrop-blur-xl shadow-[0_40px_60px_-5px_rgba(54,59,16,0.06)]">
    <div class="flex justify-between items-center max-w-[1618px] mx-auto px-6 lg:px-[5.5rem] h-24">
      <a href="/" class="text-3xl font-black text-primary px-6 font-headline tracking-tight">
        Gaia
      </a>
      <div class="hidden md:flex items-center gap-12 font-headline tracking-tight font-bold uppercase text-sm">
        <a class="text-on-surface/70 hover:text-on-surface transition-colors" href="/">Inicio</a>
        <a class="text-on-surface/70 hover:text-on-surface transition-colors" href="/hub">Hub</a>
        <a class="text-on-surface/70 hover:text-on-surface transition-colors" href="/market">Market</a>
        <a class="text-on-surface/70 hover:text-on-surface transition-colors" href="/commons">Commons</a>
        <div class="relative group">
          <a class="text-primary border-b-2 border-primary pb-1 flex items-center gap-1" href="/commons">
            Impact
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">expand_more</span>
          </a>
          <div class="absolute top-full left-0 pt-2 opacity-0 invisible group-hover:opacity-100 group-hover:visible transition-all duration-200">
            <div class="bg-white/95 backdrop-blur-xl rounded-xl shadow-xl border border-outline/10 py-2 min-w-[180px]">
              <a class="block px-4 py-2 text-primary bg-surface-container transition-colors text-xs" href="/commons/impact-fund/">Impact Fund</a>
              <a class="block px-4 py-2 text-on-surface/70 hover:text-primary hover:bg-surface-container transition-colors text-xs" href="/commons/impact-hub/">Impact Hub</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
        <a href="#comunidad" class="bg-primary text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-full font-headline font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-wider hover:opacity-90 transition-all scale-95 active:scale-90">
          Únete
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <main class="pt-32">
    <!-- Hero Section: Solar Alchemy -->
    <section class="px-6 lg:px-[5.5rem] py-16 lg:py-32 max-w-[1618px] mx-auto">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-[1.618fr_1fr] gap-12 lg:gap-16 items-center">
        <div class="space-y-8">
          <span class="inline-block px-4 py-2 bg-secondary-container text-on-secondary-container rounded-full text-xs font-bold tracking-widest uppercase font-label">
            Gaia Impact Fund
          </span>
          <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl lg:text-8xl font-black font-headline text-on-surface leading-[0.9] tracking-tighter">
            Capital al servicio de <span class="text-primary italic">la vida</span>.
          </h1>
          <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-on-surface/70 font-light max-w-xl leading-relaxed">
            El dinero no es el problema. El problema es hacia dónde fluye. Redirigimos la riqueza hacia la regeneración planetaria.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 pt-4">
            <a href="#comunidad" class="solar-gradient text-white px-10 py-5 rounded-xl font-headline font-extrabold text-sm tracking-wider uppercase shadow-xl hover:translate-y-[-4px] transition-all">
              Hablar con el Equipo
            </a>
            <a href="#" class="bg-surface-container-high text-on-surface px-10 py-5 rounded-xl font-headline font-bold text-sm tracking-wider uppercase border border-outline/20 hover:bg-surface-container transition-all">
              Descargar Brochure
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="relative group">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-primary/20 blur-[100px] rounded-full group-hover:bg-primary/30 transition-all duration-700"></div>
          <div class="relative aspect-[1/1.618] rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl">
            <img 
              class="w-full h-full object-cover grayscale-[20%] hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-1000 scale-105 group-hover:scale-100" 
              alt="Mountain valley with sunlight" 
              src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1506905925346-21bda4d32df4?q=80&w=2070&auto=format&fit=crop"
            />
            <div class="absolute bottom-8 left-8 right-8 bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-md p-6 rounded-lg border border-white/20">
              <p class="text-white font-headline font-bold text-sm tracking-tight">ACTIVOS BAJO GESTIÓN</p>
              <p class="text-white text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-black">$2.6B+ REGENERATIVOS</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Definition & Strategic Heart -->
    <section class="bg-surface-container-low py-24 lg:py-32">
      <div class="px-6 lg:px-[5.5rem] max-w-[1618px] mx-auto text-center space-y-12">
        <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto space-y-6">
          <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline font-black tracking-tight text-on-surface">El Fondo Estratégico</h2>
          <p class="text-xl text-on-surface/70 font-medium leading-relaxed">
            Gaia no es solo un repositorio de capital. Es el corazón estratégico que moviliza y despliega recursos hacia la regeneración ecológica a gran escala.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-4 pt-16">
          <!-- Mechanism Cards -->
          <div class="bg-white p-8 lg:p-10 rounded-xl space-y-6 text-left border border-outline/10 hover:shadow-2xl transition-all group">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-primary-container/30 flex items-center justify-center group-hover:bg-primary-container transition-colors">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-3xl">add_circle</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold font-headline">Agrega</h3>
            <p class="text-on-surface/60 text-sm leading-relaxed">Consolidamos capital fragmentado en un motor de inversión de alto impacto.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white p-8 lg:p-10 rounded-xl space-y-6 text-left border border-outline/10 hover:shadow-2xl transition-all group">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-secondary-container/30 flex items-center justify-center group-hover:bg-secondary-container transition-colors">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-secondary text-3xl">hub</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold font-headline">Orquesta</h3>
            <p class="text-on-surface/60 text-sm leading-relaxed">Asignación inteligente de recursos basada en bio-prioridades territoriales.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white p-8 lg:p-10 rounded-xl space-y-6 text-left border border-outline/10 hover:shadow-2xl transition-all group">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-tertiary-container/30 flex items-center justify-center group-hover:bg-tertiary-container transition-colors">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-tertiary text-3xl">bolt</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold font-headline">Acelera</h3>
            <p class="text-on-surface/60 text-sm leading-relaxed">Impulsamos iniciativas críticas que requieren despliegue rápido de liquidez.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white p-8 lg:p-10 rounded-xl space-y-6 text-left border border-outline/10 hover:shadow-2xl transition-all group">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-surface-variant flex items-center justify-center group-hover:bg-outline transition-colors">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-on-surface text-3xl">balance</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold font-headline">Alinea</h3>
            <p class="text-on-surface/60 text-sm leading-relaxed">Garantizamos que cada centavo respete los principios de soberanía ecosistémica.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Capital Flow: Dashboard Style Visualization -->
    <section class="px-6 lg:px-[5.5rem] py-24 lg:py-32 max-w-[1618px] mx-auto overflow-hidden">
      <div class="mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline font-black tracking-tight">Mecánica de Flujo</h2>
        <p class="text-on-surface/60 text-lg mt-4">La ruta del capital hacia el impacto real.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-stretch gap-4 min-h-[400px] lg:min-h-[500px]">
        <div class="flex-1 bg-surface-container-high p-8 lg:p-12 rounded-xl flex flex-col justify-between border-l-8 border-primary">
          <span class="text-primary font-black text-5xl lg:text-6xl">01</span>
          <div>
            <h4 class="text-2xl font-bold font-headline mb-2">Principios</h4>
            <p class="text-on-surface/60">Filtrado ético y regenerativo de toda entrada de capital.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex-1 bg-surface-container p-8 lg:p-12 rounded-xl flex flex-col justify-between border-l-8 border-primary-container">
          <span class="text-primary-container font-black text-5xl lg:text-6xl">02</span>
          <div>
            <h4 class="text-2xl font-bold font-headline mb-2">Capital Estratégico</h4>
            <p class="text-on-surface/60">Agrupación de fondos soberanos, institucionales y privados.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex-1 bg-surface-container-low p-8 lg:p-12 rounded-xl flex flex-col justify-between border-l-8 border-secondary">
          <span class="text-secondary font-black text-5xl lg:text-6xl">03</span>
          <div>
            <h4 class="text-2xl font-bold font-headline mb-2">Fondos Especializados</h4>
            <p class="text-on-surface/60">Vehículos específicos por bioma: Selva, Océano, Suelo Vivo.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex-1 bg-white p-8 lg:p-12 rounded-xl flex flex-col justify-between border-l-8 border-secondary-fixed">
          <span class="text-secondary-fixed font-black text-5xl lg:text-6xl">04</span>
          <div>
            <h4 class="text-2xl font-bold font-headline mb-2">Impacto Real</h4>
            <p class="text-on-surface/60">Proyectos tangibles con métricas de regeneración verificadas.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Why Invest: Asymmetric Bento Grid -->
    <section class="bg-surface py-24 lg:py-32 border-t border-outline/10">
      <div class="px-6 lg:px-[5.5rem] max-w-[1618px] mx-auto">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 md:grid-rows-2 gap-6 lg:gap-8">
          <div class="md:col-span-8 bg-surface-container-highest rounded-xl p-10 lg:p-16 flex flex-col justify-center space-y-6">
            <h3 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-headline font-bold">Por qué invertir con Gaia</h3>
            <p class="text-xl text-on-surface/60 max-w-xl">No es solo filantropía, es la creación de la infraestructura económica del siglo XXI. El valor real reside en la resiliencia biológica.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="md:col-span-4 bg-primary-container p-10 lg:p-12 rounded-xl flex flex-col justify-end group">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-on-primary-container text-5xl lg:text-6xl mb-8 group-hover:rotate-12 transition-transform">trending_up</span>
            <h4 class="text-2xl font-black font-headline text-on-primary-container">Retorno Múltiple</h4>
            <p class="text-on-primary-container/80 mt-2">Financiero, ecológico, social y sistémico.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="md:col-span-4 bg-secondary-container p-10 lg:p-12 rounded-xl flex flex-col justify-end group">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-on-secondary-container text-5xl lg:text-6xl mb-8 group-hover:-translate-y-2 transition-transform">foundation</span>
            <h4 class="text-2xl font-black font-headline text-on-secondary-container">Infraestructura Real</h4>
            <p class="text-on-secondary-container/80 mt-2">Propiedad compartida de activos bioproductivos.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="md:col-span-8 bg-inverse-surface text-inverse-on-surface p-10 lg:p-12 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-between group overflow-hidden relative">
            <div class="relative z-10">
              <h4 class="text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-black font-headline">Posicionamiento Estratégico</h4>
              <p class="text-inverse-on-surface/60 mt-4 max-w-md">Liderazgo en la transición hacia la economía post-extractiva.</p>
            </div>
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-8xl lg:text-[120px] absolute -right-8 opacity-10 group-hover:opacity-20 transition-opacity">public</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Final CTA: The Call to Action -->
    <section id="comunidad" class="px-6 lg:px-[5.5rem] py-24 lg:py-32 max-w-[1618px] mx-auto text-center">
      <div class="bg-white py-16 lg:py-24 rounded-xl border border-outline/20 shadow-2xl relative overflow-hidden">
        <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-96 h-96 bg-primary/10 blur-[120px] rounded-full -translate-y-1/2 translate-x-1/2"></div>
        <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-96 h-96 bg-secondary/10 blur-[120px] rounded-full translate-y-1/2 -translate-x-1/2"></div>
        <div class="relative z-10 space-y-10 max-w-4xl mx-auto px-8">
          <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-7xl font-headline font-black tracking-tight leading-tight">
            Redirige tu capital.<br/>Regenera el mundo.
          </h2>
          <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-center gap-4 lg:gap-6">
            <a href="https://t.me/+1x_EVaVp-lEwN2I8" target="_blank" class="solar-gradient text-white px-10 lg:px-12 py-5 lg:py-6 rounded-xl font-headline font-black text-lg tracking-wider uppercase shadow-2xl hover:scale-105 transition-all">
              Hablar con el Equipo
            </a>
            <a href="#" class="bg-surface-container-high text-on-surface px-10 lg:px-12 py-5 lg:py-6 rounded-xl font-headline font-bold text-lg tracking-wider uppercase border border-outline/30 hover:bg-surface-container transition-all">
              Ver Portafolio Actual
            </a>
          </div>
          <p class="text-on-surface/60 font-medium pt-8">Únete a los más de 450 guardianes de capital que ya están orquestando el cambio.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <!-- Footer -->
  <footer class="w-full py-16 lg:py-24 bg-surface-container border-t border-outline/10">
    <div class="max-w-[1618px] mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-[1.618fr_1fr] gap-12 px-6 lg:px-[5.5rem]">
      <div class="space-y-8">
        <div class="font-headline font-bold text-primary text-2xl tracking-tight">
          Gaia Ecosystem
        </div>
        <p class="font-body text-sm leading-relaxed text-on-surface/60 max-w-sm">
          Infraestructura para una civilización regenerativa. Un ecosistema descentralizado de coordinación planetaria.
        </p>
        <p class="font-body text-sm text-on-surface/40">
          © 2026 Gaia Ecosystem.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-8 font-body text-sm">
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
          <span class="font-bold text-primary uppercase tracking-wider text-xs">Explorar</span>
          <a class="text-on-surface/60 hover:text-primary transition-colors" href="/hub">Gaia Hub</a>
          <a class="text-on-surface/60 hover:text-primary transition-colors" href="/market">Gaia Market</a>
          <a class="text-on-surface/60 hover:text-primary transition-colors" href="/commons">Gaia Commons</a>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
          <span class="font-bold text-primary uppercase tracking-wider text-xs">Comunidad</span>
          <a class="text-on-surface/60 hover:text-primary transition-colors" href="https://t.me/+1x_EVaVp-lEwN2I8" target="_blank">Telegram</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </footer>
</Layout>

<style>
  .material-symbols-outlined {
    font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 0, 'wght' 400, 'GRAD' 0, 'opsz' 24;
  }
  .solar-gradient {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #776300 0%, #ffd709 100%);
  }
</style>
